    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is an absolute dream! It\u2019s in seriously incredible shape\u2014honestly, it's been babied since day one. Not a scratch or a dent in sight, and the interior is just pristine. It drives so smoothly, you\u2019ll fall in love the second you get behind the wheel. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make someone very happy! Come check it out before it's gone!",
