    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera represents the pinnacle of analog feedback paired with modern reliability. Featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), the powerplant delivers linear torque across the entire rev range. The chassis is equipped with PASM for active damping, ensuring optimal contact patches during high-lateral-G maneuvers. Every component, from the Brembo-sourced monobloc calipers to the precise synchromesh of the 6-speed manual gearbox, remains in concours-level condition. Zero bore scoring, a pristine underbody, and a factory-spec alignment make this a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
