    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been meticulously garage-kept and exclusively hand-washed, the exterior is completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows absolutely no signs of creasing or wear, while the dashboard and trim pieces remain factory-perfect. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity surround sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history from authorized dealerships and exceptionally low mileage. We have recently performed a rigorous multi-point inspection and a professional concours-level detail to ensure it meets the highest possible standards. This isn't just a used car; it is a pristine, investment-quality example for the most demanding enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
